01:35.300 --> 01:37.200
I've never once seen a person

01:37.200 --> 01:39.330
flying around
on a broom stick.

01:40.870 --> 01:43.700
The way that I started
to perform magic

01:43.700 --> 01:46.030
in a locked psychiatric unit

01:46.030 --> 01:49.070
was that I wanted to get into
the field of psychology

01:49.070 --> 01:51.200
but I didn't
have any experience.

01:51.200 --> 01:53.700
I thought, what better way
to get my foot in the door

01:53.700 --> 01:55.130
then to volunteer.

01:55.130 --> 01:58.270
Magic is a great way
to demonstrate to someone

01:58.270 --> 02:00.230
