02:04.130 --> 02:08.699
I continue to use magic
in my work now as a therapist

02:08.699 --> 02:12.070
to help people learn about how
they misperceive reality,

02:12.070 --> 02:16.430
and I working to help expose
and destroy that illusion.

02:21.500 --> 02:24.370
- Please welcome,
Tyler Twombly.

02:30.770 --> 02:32.830
- Penn.
Teller.

02:32.830 --> 02:35.330
Alyson.
People.

02:35.330 --> 02:37.900
I've come here
to share with you a secret.

02:37.900 --> 02:40.300
There is enormous potential
for magic

02:40.300 --> 02:44.030
in the world
of office supplies.

02:44.030 --> 02:46.230
Countless grand illusions
have been performed

02:46.230 --> 02:49.430
with mighty skill
on this large stage,

02:49.430 --> 02:51.500
