to come in very close.

03:07.070 --> 03:09.000
For your effort, however,
you'll be rewarded

03:09.000 --> 03:10.970
because what you will see
will change the way

03:10.970 --> 03:13.330
you look at these little pieces
of paper forever

03:13.330 --> 03:15.130
and prove that
the greatest magic

03:15.130 --> 03:17.730
happens at the smallest scale.

03:17.730 --> 03:20.300
So with that,
I'd like to invite Alyson

03:20.300 --> 03:22.570
to join me over here.
Thank you very much.

03:24.300 --> 03:26.100
- Hi.
- Hello, Alyson.

03:26.100 --> 03:28.730
Please stand right there.

03:28.730 --> 03:31.200
Now, Alyson.
- Yes.

03:31.200 --> 03:32.930
