04:43.800 --> 04:45.700
And we'll put a little bird
in the sky just to give it

04:45.700 --> 04:47.230
a little sense of depth,
don't you think?

04:47.230 --> 04:48.900
- Nice.
- Yeah.

04:48.900 --> 04:51.900
Two hearts,
at one point separated,

04:51.900 --> 04:54.630
by space and time
until one day,

04:54.630 --> 04:56.430
everything changed.
- Oh.

04:56.430 --> 04:57.970
- That's what
we're gonna do right now.

04:57.970 --> 05:00.870
We're gonna bring
those hearts together.

05:04.900 --> 05:07.530
- Aw.

05:09.970 --> 05:12.230
- That is for you.
- Thank you.

05:12.230 --> 05:13.570
- Thank you very much.
- All right.

05:13.570 --> 05:15.570
- It would be my greatest honor
if that one day

05:15.570 --> 05:17.970
wound up on your refrigerator.
- Perfect.

05:17.970 --> 05:19.370
- Thank you so much.
- Thank you.

05:19.370 --> 05:20.800
- Thank you so much.
You can go back.

05:22.770 --> 05:25.170
Thank you.

