but I'm sensing
a little skepticism

05:31.400 --> 05:34.370
emanating
from this general area.

05:34.370 --> 05:35.630
Yes.

05:35.630 --> 05:37.670
The gentlemen in the suits.

05:37.670 --> 05:38.930
Uh, Teller.

05:38.930 --> 05:41.630
Could you please
join me up here on stage?

05:43.270 --> 05:45.500
Thank you very much.

05:47.330 --> 05:49.930
Thank you very much.

05:49.930 --> 05:51.900
Thank you for joining me.
