06:22.400 --> 06:24.930
Once you've thought of it.

06:24.930 --> 06:27.570
- C.

06:27.570 --> 06:29.330
- He can speak.

06:31.270 --> 06:34.430
Now we're gonna place
that dream inside

06:34.430 --> 06:36.470
a perfect little bubble.

06:40.470 --> 06:42.730
Eh, not totally perfect,

06:42.730 --> 06:44.570
