06:44.570 --> 06:47.630
This is Teller's dream.

06:47.630 --> 06:51.370
And this is where
we start to tell our story.

06:51.370 --> 06:54.630
Now in the beginning,
a dream is just a dream.

06:54.630 --> 06:56.000
It doesn't go anywhere.

06:56.000 --> 06:59.830
Until that initial exertion
of effort sends it off

06:59.830 --> 07:02.600
in some direction.

07:02.600 --> 07:04.530
Then you gotta
make some choices.

07:08.400 --> 07:09.870
You probably made some choices.

07:09.870 --> 07:12.470
Some good,
some maybe questionable.

07:12.470 --> 07:14.100
Sends it off in yet another.

07:14.100 --> 07:16.330
But then,
through a series of events,

07:16.330 --> 07:18.800
both serendipitous and planned,

07:18.800 --> 07:22.530
we wind up where we are
right here today.

07:22.530 --> 07:24.970
This is for you.

07:24.970 --> 07:26.900
And this is just
one single page

07:26.900 --> 07:29.670
in the story so far.
Thank you very much.

07:29.670 --> 07:32.400
Thank you so much.

07:32.400 --> 07:35.870
Thank you.
- Tyler Twombly.

07:40.200 --> 07:43.030
Hi, again.
- Hello.

07:43.030 --> 07:45.470
- Well, you had me
when you had a marker

07:45.470 --> 07:48.400
'cause I just love any sort
