08:09.700 --> 08:12.430
- Well, I didn't think

08:12.430 --> 08:15.570
that I would ever do a show

08:15.570 --> 08:18.700
like this, but here I am.

08:18.700 --> 08:20.770
Surprise.

08:23.900 --> 08:25.900
- So do you think you'll fool
