08:37.500 --> 08:39.870
- All right, well, it's time
to go to Penn and Teller.

08:39.870 --> 08:41.770
Let's see
if you fooled them or not.

08:41.770 --> 08:43.600
- All right.
- Yeah.

08:43.600 --> 08:45.600
- Uh, you know,
you told the truth, Tyler,

08:45.600 --> 08:46.830
