you're using,

09:07.230 --> 09:11.270
but we believe that everything
you're using, we see.

09:11.270 --> 09:13.770
It comes from the--
it comes from the Post-it pad.

09:13.770 --> 09:15.200
It's really--
it's really fabulous.

09:15.200 --> 09:18.870
And, uh, we also love the fact
that it deals with love

09:18.870 --> 09:20.800
and how hearts can move around.

09:20.800 --> 09:22.970
You know, you love one person
then love another

09:22.970 --> 09:24.870
and things move
from one place to the other.

09:24.870 --> 09:27.130
It also made me think of, um,

09:27.130 --> 09:29.600
you know, still haven't found
