through school with magic.

11:17.700 --> 11:20.000
I really like doing
coin magic in the hospital

11:20.000 --> 11:21.670
because a little boy
or girl comes in

11:21.670 --> 11:23.800
worried about
their sick dog or cat,

11:23.800 --> 11:26.270
and all I have to do is pull
a coin out of that dog's ear

11:26.270 --> 11:28.400
and their frown
turns into a smile.

11:28.400 --> 11:30.300
Dogs and cats can't tell you
what's going on.

11:30.300 --> 11:32.800
You have to figure that out,
and that's the challenge.

11:32.800 --> 11:35.130
The challenge of magic
is to find a new way

11:35.130 --> 11:37.970
to do an effect that makes it
look even more impressive.

11:37.970 --> 11:40.970
I like to tell people that
I have a love of magic

11:40.970 --> 11:42.700
but my life
is veterinary medicine.

11:42.700 --> 11:44.030
Not bad for a day's work,
right?

