You walk through the doors
of this theater

12:29.270 --> 12:31.970
and enter
a magical dimension.

12:31.970 --> 12:35.330
A dimension of Penn.
A dimension of Teller.

12:35.330 --> 12:37.930
A dimension of
prestidigitation.

12:37.930 --> 12:40.030
You're put into
a suggestive state

12:40.030 --> 12:42.000
of smoke and mirrors.

12:42.000 --> 12:45.470
You just punched your ticket
for the "Fool Us" Zone.

