dismissed as tales of fantasy

13:06.600 --> 13:08.670
left to be told
to gullible children,

13:08.670 --> 13:11.970
there exists within each
of them a modicum of truth,

13:11.970 --> 13:14.200
and to that I point you
toward an incident

13:14.200 --> 13:16.830
which occurred back in 1931.

13:16.830 --> 13:19.600
The place, a street
in the center of London,

13:19.600 --> 13:21.270
and if you were to
look through the crowd

13:21.270 --> 13:24.200
