a man shining shoes.

13:24.200 --> 13:25.730
That man is George Midas.

13:25.730 --> 13:28.800
A poor man beat down by
the hardships of his life.

13:28.800 --> 13:31.870
But in a few brief moments,
that life will change.

13:31.870 --> 13:33.730
