a coin of gold.

15:11.900 --> 15:14.130
Solid gold.

15:14.130 --> 15:16.800
But as George played around
with that shiny, gold penny....

15:16.800 --> 15:19.400
He stopped thinking of all
of the good and wondrous things

15:19.400 --> 15:22.100
he was going to do
for his family. For you see,

15:22.100 --> 15:24.600
George now realized
that he had the power.

15:24.600 --> 15:26.430
And he was going
to use that power

15:26.430 --> 15:29.270
not for good, but to get back
at all of the people

15:29.270 --> 15:30.670
who beat him down

15:30.670 --> 15:32.900
and put him
into a state of poverty.

15:32.900 --> 15:35.470
And at that very moment,
at that very moment,

15:35.470 --> 15:38.830
that shiny gold penny
changed back...

15:38.830 --> 15:41.500
to copper.

15:41.500 --> 15:44.370
When George saw what had
happened his smile faded,

15:44.370 --> 15:47.600
for he realized that the magic
had only been fleeting.

15:47.600 --> 15:50.770
And in fact, when he took
a look back into his cup...

15:52.130 --> 15:53.500
he found that
all of the shiny gold

15:53.500 --> 15:56.530
had changed back to copper.

15:56.530 --> 15:58.530
And as George
looked on in despair...

15:58.530 --> 16:01.870
It was as if you could hear
the voice of Rod Serling,

16:01.870 --> 16:04.870
who said,
"Yes, George Midas,

16:04.870 --> 16:08.270
a man who possessed
a true gift.

16:08.270 --> 16:11.500
A real Midas touch.

16:11.500 --> 16:13.270
But gifts used
for the wrong reasons,

16:13.270 --> 16:17.030
can also be taken away
back to the refund counters

16:17.030 --> 16:20.700
found only in the stores
of the 'Fool Us' Zone."

16:20.700 --> 16:22.330
Thank you.

16:23.900 --> 16:27.300
- Dr. Michael Rubinstein.

16:27.300 --> 16:30.830
Ooh, hi, nice to meet you.

16:30.830 --> 16:33.900
