A three,
a red three.

31:34.170 --> 31:36.970
Now if it's red,
it could be diamonds

31:36.970 --> 31:38.930
or it could be hearts.

31:38.930 --> 31:40.370
Is it hearts?

31:40.370 --> 31:44.470
H-E-A-R-T-S.

31:47.000 --> 31:48.900
It is hearts.

31:48.900 --> 31:51.200
Maybe.

