32:03.500 --> 32:05.930
but if this were true,
it's saying your card, Teller,

32:05.930 --> 32:08.970
was the red three of hearts.

32:08.970 --> 32:13.130
So the match would be
the other red three.

32:13.130 --> 32:16.770
The red three of diamonds.

32:20.170 --> 32:23.930
That's what I call artificial
intelligence right--right there.

32:23.930 --> 32:27.170
And you chose
the red three of hearts.

32:33.670 --> 32:37.000
Now, we've said that Siri
can answer the question.

32:37.000 --> 32:39.670
I can refine my question
conversationally.

32:39.670 --> 32:41.800
Is it red?
Is it diamonds?

32:41.800 --> 32:44.670
But we also said,
